                                                                                                                                Data and tables

                                                                                                                                Charts

                                                                                                                                Charts is a global library for data visualization that provides reusable, flexible chart modules that can be used across all platforms and lines of business.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Charts by concepts
                                                                                                                                Chart colors
                                                                                                                                Base charts library

                                                                                                                                Anatomy

                                                                                                                                Each chart is made up of a sum of parts, each part being its own individual module that is swappable for maximum customizability. Custom charts can also be built by snapping different parts together.

                                                                                                                                You'll need to decide what gridlines and axes, and you might not need to include a title or a legend depending on the data and chart environment.

                                                                                                                                Gridlines

                                                                                                                                • Dual Gridlines

                                                                                                                                • Dotted lines

                                                                                                                                • Label position

                                                                                                                                Labels

                                                                                                                                When adding labels, provide enough room, so the labels don't overlap. Alternatively, you can surface labels only when interacting with the chart if space is tight.

                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Do not let the labels overlap each other
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Ensure there is enough room for the labels
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Surface the labels when interacting with the chart


                                                                                                                                Axes

                                                                                                                                • Axis alignment

                                                                                                                                • Tick marks

                                                                                                                                Legend

                                                                                                                                • Line

                                                                                                                                • Square

                                                                                                                                • Circle


                                                                                                                                Usage

                                                                                                                                Choosing the right chart

                                                                                                                                This step is arguably the hardest step in the process, but we have set up Base Charts in a way that will ideally guide you to make a more accurate choice. We encourage you to get into the habit of using the questions below to narrow down your options. See also Chart types and Charts by concept.


                                                                                                                                What concept are your users trying to understand?


                                                                                                                                How many variables do you need to show?

                                                                                                                                Is seeing the data change over time important?

                                                                                                                                Once you know how you’d like to show the data, you can start building the environment that best fits the visualization. Think about how to make the data easy to understand at a glance. If it’s more complex than usual, focus on making the data clear and decipherable.

                                                                                                                                Data table
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                A Data table is a type of data display optimized for medium-to-large, rich data that users might want to analyze as a whole.
